name: SIGIL OF POWER
description:
We seek all manner of power: physical and psychological; divine or obscure; seen or unseen, and acquiring it usually comes only after many sacrifices.  Strength and power pulsate through this sigil, emanating enough arcane energy to power up a small town.
Join all other humans in a endless quest to best ourselves.

[Based on Yujiro Hanma's Demon Back from the manga Baki the Grappler] 

800x800gif mousedrawn on a Deluxe Paint emulator for the MS-DOS
